      <content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/2023/11/26/test-post/">&lt;p&gt;The Cybercat blog website is based on the &lt;a href=&quot;https://jekyllthemes.io/theme/whiteglass&quot;&gt;Whiteglass&lt;/a&gt; theme.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;TOC &lt;!-- omit in toc --&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#workflow&quot;&gt;Workflow&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;ul&gt;
